What is JSX, and why is it used?
JSX er full meaning hocche Javascript XML. XML hocche ek dhoroner syntax extension Javascript er jonno, jeta HTML er moto markup shorashori use korte dey


What is the difference between State and Props?
Props e external data pass kora hoye thake parent theke child component er moddhe, ar state nijer moddhe data manage kore thake useState hook baa setState method babohar kore
State er moddhe mostly user input, form data, timer etc pass kora hoy.


What is the useState hook, and how does it work?
eita react er ek dhoroner special function jeita data er change time er shathe track kore thake.

How can you share state between components in React?
parent component e useState hook babohar kore


How is event handling done in React?
camelCase naming method use kore button e onClick={handleClick}